---
title: Chipotle Chicken Flatbreads with Poblano Pepper, Mexican Cheese, and Cilantro
description: This is the *other* way to get a taste of the Southwest, one that doesn’t involve a tortilla, but a nice and toasty flatbread. Toppings like chipotle-spiced chicken, poblano pepper, and a blend of Mexican cheeses make it a winner in the flavor department. But the bread is basically a pizza crust by a different name, becoming warm, crisp, and tasty after only 5 minutes in the oven.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/w35-r5-9da67c19.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/chipotle-chicken-flatbreads-5b47a2bfae08b52bce102032-d5589dc9.pdf
time required: 20 minutes
course: main course
servings: 2
cuisine: North America
